to smuggle arms.

58
00:19:10,939 --> 00:19:13,703  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:479
He used to work for Hui, but that
ended when Johnny Wong bought him out.

59
00:19:13,842 --> 00:19:16,902  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:479
