that respect and face are vital.

109
00:24:38,433 --> 00:24:42,665  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:479
l'm old-fashioned.
-lt works, though. We respect you.

110
00:24:46,108 --> 00:24:51,239  X1:000 X2:719 Y1:002 Y2:479
